programme.desc: Shipwreck and Snake Eyes continue to evade capture in an effort to get back to the Joe team with vital data about Cobra's control cubes.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.sub-title: The Further Adventures Of G.I. Joe - Day 3 : Three Cubes To Darkness
programme.desc: As three of Cobra's relay cubes are activated, Cobra commander moves forward with his plans to activate the fourth and final cube in the sea of lost souls. Meanwhile, Shipwreck and Snake Eyes escape Cobra's troopers in Enterprise City.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.sub-title: The Further Adventures Of G.I. Joe - Day 4 : Chaos In The Sea Of Lost Souls
programme.desc: Cobra commander activates the pyramid of darkness, stranding not only the JOES but also his comrades the crimson twins. Always prepared with a backup plan, Tomax and Xamot have other designs for the pyramid and Cobra.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.sub-title: The Further Adventures Of G.I. Joe - Day 5 : Knotting Cobra's Coils
programme.desc: Chaos ensues as the leaders of Cobra struggle for control of the pyramid of darkness. As Cobra forces battle each other, the Joe team is able to regain control of space station delta and launch a full-scale assault to try to destroy the Pyramid.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Zartan, disguised as a notable French scientist, infiltrates the worldwide defense center on a mission to destroy the facility for Cobra. He's planted a bomb, and now the clock is ticking can the Joe team find and defuse the bomb before it's too late?

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Cobra uses Tomax and Xamot's company extensive enterprises to purchase the Red Rocket food chain and use its location as a network of secret missile launching bases. But the JOE team catches on to the conspiracy.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: When a secret military satellite is forced out of orbit by Cobra, the Joe team races to its location before Cobra can get their hands on it. But both the Joes and Cobra find that a third party has entered the battle for the device.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: In a diabolical plan to control the world's fuel supplies, Cobra begins detonating oil tankers and pipelines by remote. But when sparks uncovers the frequency Cobra is using to destroy the tankers, the Joe team may be able to turn the tables on them!

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Cobra steals an experimental nitrogen rocket fuel. But before the Joes can capture the crimson guard in possession of the fuel, he hides it in a greenhouse, where the volatile mixture mutates everything into gigantic man-killing plants.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Cobra threatens to use their latest weapon, the Ion attractor, to pull down the aurora borealis, melt the polar ice caps and flood the world. With every costal city in danger, the Joes head to the north pole to try to put a stop to it.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.desc: Marty and Underworld Marty swap places on Halloween, Underworld Marty goes trick-or-treating with Burnie and Holly, while real Marty is trapped below, where the underworldly inhabitants want to make a meal of him.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.desc: Burnie and Marty discover that everyone in ToonVille hates when they're together. Blaming each other for their unlikableness, they end their friendship. Marty then skyrockets to success, and Burnie sinks into the gutter.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.desc: When Super Simon has to go and do his scout badges, Marty is thrilled to help him. But Super Simon takes all the credit and Marty gets jealous and sabotages his hero forgetting the true meaning of ToonScouts.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.sub-title: You Can't Handle the Tooth / Marty the Monster
programme.desc: When Marty gets a gold-grill after losing his teeth, he becomes super cool and hangs out with Super Simon and his cool guy posse. But he gets bored of them and tries everything to hang with Burnie and Holly again.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.sub-title: Robogirl AKA Logic Police / Chef and the Marty Show
programme.desc: Holly's logic board jammed and she vows to destroy all toons because they're illogical. She turns ToonVille into real things, until Marty puts on a toon display of unmatched proportions. A display so toony it saves ToonVille.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.sub-title: Marty's Exploding Head / How Marty Got his Toon Back
programme.desc: Marty gets so smart that his head expands. Dr. Smartypants tells Holly and Burnie that if he learns one more thing his head will explode. While keeping all new information from him, they try to bring him back to normal.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.desc: When Marty takes over the doctor's annual job of recalibrating the toons, he and Suki make a mess of things. Marty races against the clock to get their calibrations to stop ToonVille from exploding into the toon-abyss.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.sub-title: The Hat makes the Toon / To Be Continued
programme.desc: When Marty's hat is stolen by Hobo Jeb, everyone thinks Hobo Jeb is Marty! Holly and Marty have to get the toons to look past the superficial. And when that doesn't work, well, he has to steal his hat and identity back.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.desc: Marty is super extra good at being Burnatron's evil sidekick, so good in fact that he alienates his best friend Burnie.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.desc: After an open call to find the New Face of the ToonMart, Burnie becomes the new ToonMart Mascot, and Marty his mentor, until Burnie gets bored and overworked and sabotages himself.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.sub-title: Where There's Smoke There's Marty / The Suit Makes de Super Hero
programme.desc: Marty's overworked cartoon exit-smoke trail leaves in a huff, leaving him without energy. He borrows Burnie's smoke trail to compete for the Employee of the Month award.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.desc: Marty, out to prove all ToonMart gizmos work perfectly, helps Chef catch Chicken. When he roasts Chicken, the toons ostracize him and he learns that everyone has their place and that saucy Chicken's not really dead.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.sub-title: The Barber of Toonville / Rest in Pieces
programme.desc: When Burnie gets the worst (and only) haircut ever in the history of ToonVille, Burnie's hair clippings go on a cultural crime spree while Marty's lost hair goes on a lonely quest to be reunited with his owner.

programme.title: Toon Marty
programme.desc: Marty and Underworld Marty swap places on Halloween, Underworld Marty goes trick-or-treating with Burnie and Holly, while real Marty is trapped below, where the underworldly inhabitants want to make a meal of him.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: When the Baroness acquires a legendary conch and uses its mind-controlling siren song on all the males among Joe and Cobra's ranks, it's up to Scarlett, Lady Jaye and Cover Girl to end her reign of terror.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Tokyo is the site of a world economic conference - and Cobra's latest target for chaos. When Cobra devises a plan to destroy the whole city with an earthquake, the Joes are sent in to stop them.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Part 1 of 2. When G.I. Joe captures a secret Cobra explosive, Cobra responds by kidnapping several Joe family members and brainwashing them into fighting a battle for its return. It's a strike force the Joes are afraid to fight or harm.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Part 2 of 2. The Joes are caught off-balance when their very families and personal lives are used against them. To defeat Cobra, retrieve the explosive, and rescue their loved ones, the Joes not only have to be tough, but creative too.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: While on a camping trip, Bazooka watches a monstrous creature rise from the water and devour what looks like a giant firefly. Unfortunately, none of the Joes believe him, until it's revealed that this "sea serpent" is a Cobra-built submarine!

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: After an air duel, Storm Shadow crashes into a lake in the north of Britain. He's rescued from his sinking plane by an apparition who guides him to the legendary sword Excalibur resting on the lake bottom. With the sword, Storm Shadow will be unstoppable!

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Part 1 of 2. Disillusioned by constant battle, Stealer is ready to resign from the Joe team. He gains new perspective when a Cobra weapon malfunctions and opens a rift between realities, throwing him and the Joes into a world where Cobra is in control.

programme.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
programme.desc: Part 2 of 2. Trapped in the alternate Cobra - controlled world, the Joes find an unlikely ally in the Baroness. With her help, Stealer, Clutch and the others search for a way back to their own reality. But Cobra is closing in
